  "text": "Additionally, the data structures and implementation of the algorithm are done in constant time by using the methods of Fiduccia and Mattheyses [CITATION_1] . Fiduccia and Mattheyses gave a simplification of the Kernighan-Lin heuristic that has time complexity Θ(E) [CITATION_2] . The efficiency is gained by sorting vertex gains using a method called the bucket sort. The addition of the Fiduccia-Mattheyses technique grants the ability to perform a limited, low cost, local search when solving various graph bisection problems.",
